{"name": "odoo14-addon-hr-attendance-reason", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-hr-attendance-reason", "version": "14.0.1.1.4", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Lesser General Public License v3 (LGPLv3)", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/hr-attendance", "license": "LGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "HR Attendance Reason", "upload_time": 1698500382}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-LGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: LGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fhr--attendance-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/hr-attendance\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/hr-attendance/tree/14.0/hr_attendance_reason\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/hr-attendance-14-0/hr-attendance-14-0-hr_attendance_reason\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/hr-attendance&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# HR Attendance Reason\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:e296ed667dccd9d2002778dd2100f7f415bda8c04732747cc800183fbdad82b3\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows to define reasons why the attendance is not what expected.\nSome example reasons are\n\n- Could not access the system: Visit a customer\n- Leave soon to pick up children\n- The Hr manager amended the attendance and needs to tell\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n1. Go to *Attendances > Configuration*.\n2. Create the reasons that may cause attendances to be shorter or longer\n   than normal\n3. When that situation occurs employees can justify the reason\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/hr-attendance/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/hr-attendance/issues/new?body=module:%20hr_attendance_reason%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Odoo S.A.\n- Tecnativa\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Odoo S.A.\n\n- Aaron Henriquez \\<<mailto:ahforgeflow@forgeflow.com>>\n\n- Damien Crier \\<<mailto:damien.crier@camtocamp.com>>\n\n- Saran Lim. \\<<mailto:saranl@ecosoft.co.th>>\n\n- [Tecnativa](https://www.tecnativa.com):\n\n  - V\u00edctor Mart\u00ednez\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/hr-attendance](https://github.com/OCA/hr-attendance/tree/14.0/hr_attendance_reason) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason", "documentation": ["Copyright 2017 Odoo S.A.", "Copyright 2018 ForgeFlow, S.L.", "License LGPL-3 - See http://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0.html"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason._description", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason._order", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason._sql_constraints", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason.sequence", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason.company_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason.name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason.code", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason.action_type", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.hr_attendance_reason.models.hr_attendance_reason.HrAttendanceReason.show_on_attendance_screen", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "d